{
  "text": "Note. The first crystal structure of a human pathogenic TCR in complex with HLA-A2-InsS15-23 has been determined, and the TCR orientation with respect to the HLA-A2-peptide complex is diagonal [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
  "correct_citation": {
